    <summary>Autonomous continuous development orchestrator for Claude Code</summary>
    <description>
Radioactive Ralph is a per-repo meta-orchestrator that keeps a fleet of
Claude subprocesses alive, focused, and productive across days of
autonomous development work.
    </description>
    <tags>claude ai orchestrator automation cli</tags>
    <releaseNotes>https://github.com/jbcom/radioactive-ralph/releases/tag/v0.6.0</releaseNotes>
